  "description": "A long exposure nighttime photograph showcases a suspension bridge silhouetted against a dark, moody sky. The bridge is illuminated with warm yellow lights that trace its cables and towers. In the distance, a lower, smaller bridge can be seen, also faintly lit. The scene is framed by dark, out-of-focus foliage on both sides, creating a natural vignette. The water below is calm and reflects some of the ambient light. The overall effect is atmospheric and serene.",
